name: Tabletop Biofuel Fireplace, Ethanol Portable Fireplace, Campfire, Liquid fuel Fireplace, Flame
description:
This is the liquid fuel fireplace that rests on any stable surface and provides the color, charm, and comfort of a wood-burning fire without smoke, smells, or sparks. 

Using recycled liquid ethanol fuel that gives off only water vapor and carbon dioxide, the clean-burning, portable fireplace yields a bright yellow, orange, and red 7"-high flame that flickers without fumes, making it suitable for indoor or outdoor use. 

The fireplace’s stainless steel burner unit sits between 4 panes of glass.

18 cm H x 20 cm W x 20 cm D
Burner volume: 50 ml Bio-Ethanol.

What's in the box:

Circum Fireplace - 1pc.
Damper Tool - 1pc.
Fuel not included!
